@node play "The game: Installation/Playing"

                             Installation

  The installation is very simple, just place 'Tribullation' where
you want on your hard drive, floppy disk, Ram Disk, etc. No other
files or Libraries are needed. However, your Workbench must have at
least 8 colours.

                             How to play?

  To play, click on any bubble that is next to one or more bubbles
of the same colour, these bubbles will blow up and you will get
points according to the number of blown up bubbles, as the
following table indicates:

  2 bubbles = 1 point
  3 bubbles = 3 points
  4 bubbles = 6 points
  5 bubbles = 10 points
  etc.

  As the game progresses, blocks that have diamond shapes will
appear from time to time at the top of the pyramid. These blocks
cannot be eliminated and are only there to complicate matters a
little bit...

  The game ends when there are no bubbles of the same colour
located next to each other.

  Have fun!

  To quit the game, click on the game window's close button or
press the 'Esc' key.

@endnode

